                <p class="text-lg md:text-lg mb-8 text-indigo-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Streamline your ticket management with our powerful, intuitive platform. 
                    Track, manage, and resolve tickets efficiently.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="w-full h-24">
